I am currently working as a Memory Design Engineer at STMicroelectronics (Subcontractor via Zia Semiconductor Pvt Ltd).

HOW TO NAVIGATE:
1. Type 'ls' to see the directories (experience, projects, etc.).
2. Type 'cd experience' to go into that folder.
3. Type 'ls' again to see the files.
